full_text: Did you know? VisibleSim (https://t.co/ln4qSxbDE9) is a software platform allowing the development of distributed algorithms on #modularRobots. Many modular architectures are supported: 2/3D, 4/6/8-lattice. Just try it! https://t.co/hAykgOR3Ad https://t.co/Q07UDqDkRV

Change your mind about the #robotics of tomorrow. Join @Dars2022_Sympo and find out how a #distributedsystem composed of #swarm of #robots can collaborate to accomplish complex tasks.
